"2  8-oz. boxes frozen artichoke hearts, thawed, patted dry","1/4 teaspoon crushed red pepper","4  cloves garlic, thinly sliced","6 tablespoons olive oil","  Salt and pepper","1 pound rotini pasta","1  7.5-oz. jar sun-dried tomatoes in oil, drained, thinly sliced, oil reserved","1/2  small red onion, thinly sliced (about 1/2 cup)","1/3 cup pitted green olives, sliced","1/4 cup capers, drained and rinsed","2 tablespoons red wine vinegar","1 teaspoon Dijon mustard","  Zest and 1 Tbsp. juice from 1 lemon","1/2 cup chopped, loosely packed flat-leaf parsley"